data.description: This is the one! Welcome home to 4031 Azalea Way, featuring 4,298 square feet of living space, 4 bedrooms, 4.5 bathrooms, an office, and a game room thoughtfully spread out across two levels. The wonderful chef's kitchen serves as the heart of the home and is perfect for family gatherings and entertaining guests. Downstairs primary suite is it's own private retreat, perfect for relaxing in after a productive day. En-suite primary bathroom features separate shower and tub, dual vanities, and massive walk-in closet. Situated on a .76 acre lot with beautiful landscaping and endless opportunity in the backyard for a pool, garden, sport court, or anything else you envision. The location of this home is ideal for those who want to be close to the city while still enjoying a peaceful and exclusive community. Located in the Midlothian Independent School District, known for its excellent schools. Come see all this wonderful home has to offer!
